---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<Base
  title="About - Silicon Crane"
  description="Silicon Crane helps founders and product teams validate business ideas through rapid market experiments. Learn about our mission and approach."
  ogTitle="About Silicon Crane"
  ogDescription="We help founders validate business ideas through rapid market experiments."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-crane-50 via-white to-blue-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="text-crane-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">About Us</span>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          We believe in building the right thing
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600">
          Silicon Crane exists to help founders avoid the most common startup mistake:
          building products nobody wants.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600">
            Every year, founders pour their savings, their time, and their energy into
            building products based on assumptions. Most fail not because they could not
            build what they imagined, but because they imagined the wrong thing.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
            We are on a mission to flip the script. Validate first, build second.
            Test your riskiest assumptions before you commit months of development time.
            Get real market feedback from real potential customers.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
            When you know what the market wants, you can build with confidence instead of hope.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-crane-100 to-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
          <blockquote class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 italic">
            "The only way to win is to learn faster than anyone else."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">- Eric Ries, The Lean Startup</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Values</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600">
          These principles guide everything we do.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Value 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-crane-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-crane-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Truth Over Comfort</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
            We would rather tell you your idea does not have market demand than watch you spend
            six months building something nobody wants. The market does not care about feelings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-crane-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-crane-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Speed Over Perfection</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
            A fast experiment that gives you a clear signal is worth more than a perfect
            experiment that takes too long. We optimize for learning velocity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-crane-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-crane-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Data Over Opinions</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
            Every experiment has clear success criteria defined upfront. We do not argue about
            what the results mean - we let the numbers speak.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Approach Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Approach</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600">
          We have taken the best practices from lean startup methodology, growth marketing,
          and product management and distilled them into a repeatable validation framework.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-crane-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-crane-600 font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Hypothesis-Driven</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                Every experiment starts with a clear, testable hypothesis. "We believe [customer segment]
                will [take action] because [reason]." No fuzzy thinking allowed.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-crane-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-crane-600 font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Pre-Defined Success Criteria</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                Before we start, we agree on what "good" looks like. Conversion rates, cost per lead,
                willingness to pay - whatever metrics matter for your hypothesis.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-crane-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-crane-600 font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Minimum Viable Experiment</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                We build the smallest thing that can test your hypothesis. Landing pages, not products.
                Ads, not organic growth. Speed is the competitive advantage.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-crane-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-crane-600 font-bold">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Decisive Outcomes</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                Every experiment ends with a clear recommendation: GO, KILL, or PIVOT.
                No "it depends" or "needs more research." You get actionable clarity.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Silicon Crane Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Why "Silicon Crane"?</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600">
          The crane is a symbol of patience, focus, and precision. In Japanese culture,
          it represents good fortune and longevity - earned through careful, deliberate action.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
          Like the crane, we believe in standing still to observe before making a move.
          In understanding the landscape before committing to a direction.
          In the power of patient precision over hasty action.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
          "Silicon" grounds us in the technology world we serve.
          Together, Silicon Crane represents thoughtful technology building -
          validation before velocity, understanding before action.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-crane-600">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
          Ready to validate your idea?
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-crane-100">
          Let us help you find out if customers want what you are planning to build.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <a
            href="mailto:hello@siliconcrane.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-crane-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors font-semibold text-lg shadow-lg"
          >
            Get In Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
